een tons of Protectors and a couple Sentries pop at the various spawn points.<br />There is one exception though - the 6spawn area also has a 'special' spawn which can pop a little guy named A Protector of Valor which fairly often. He drops some particularly rare loot, some of which isn't even listed on Alla's yet ;)<br />I'll have to give it a try at the 3spawn spot though, and see if I notice the increased drop rate there as you claim to see. <br />I'll let you know what I get.</span></font></td>
