                <td bgcolor="#37437B" valign="top"><font color="white" face="verdana" size="2"><small>Posted&nbsp;-&nbsp;01/31/2004&nbsp;: 06:06:36 AM</small><hr size="1"><span class="spnMessageText"> The 3spawns by SE basement drop items more often because once you kill all 3 there is a chance they will respawn as protectors, sentries, rabids, etc.  You can read up about it on the beastiary in allakhazaam.  There is a spawn cycle.  Keep all 3 killed awhile(ussually about an hour) and those guys will spawn in their place.  The wrulon sentries and protectors drop things more common than just the guards but I have seen drape of the proud off the guards.  The drops are rare even on valorous guards like the range item they drop but there is a 70k belt that drops at that camp(really rare) but it's nice to at least have a chance at winning something great and a change from the basement camp I've made about 60k in 9 hours.  I may just be getting lucky but that's what I've gotten so far and a band of risen I wear. <br /><br />When I pull the wrulons they ussually add each other but they are easy to FD split.  I had no problem with it.  The only difficult part is first kill until you get used to kiting around those columns and keeping your cycle down.  Once you do it a couple hours you will hardly ever die.  I don't even bother slowing the valorous anymore.</span></font></td>
